The paper deals with a communication problem involving encoding and decoding procedures, which are typical topics in information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also introduces a special graph for the proposed index coding problem, which is related to graph theory (cs.DS). The study of erroneous side information is a topic in signal processing (cs.SI) and error correction codes (cs.CC).
